title: A Luxury High-Rise in Downtown Dallas Area*27 Stories**4 WEEKS FREE!**
posting_body: Dallas's New High-End and Luxury 27-Story High-Rise Apartment!
Close to Dining, Shopping, Night Life, and Entertainment.
Amenities Include an Infinity Edge Pool, Two Hot Tubs, and a Lounge Area with Amazing Views of Dallas.
They also have Direct Access to The Katy Trail, a 24-Hour Concierge Desk, State of the Art Fitness Center, Roof Top Dog Park, a Dog Spa for Your Furry Friend, and So Much More.
Enjoy the Luxury of Quartz Countertops and Stainless Steel Appliances in the Kitchen.
Floor-to-Ceiling Windows, Walk-In Closets, Stand-Up Showers, Garden Tub, Wood Floors, with Washer and Dryer Included in Your Luxury High-Rise Apartment Home!
All Units have Individual Balconies all the Way up to the 27th Floor.
